{"tid":339202,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[live]獨遊台灣15日環島之旅","createTime":"2017-07-28T23:55:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-30T07:15:19.000Z","uid":130666,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8828ad79bb629f03c1513e231aaa5447ce6389b0","tid":339202,"uid":130666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T23:55:56.000Z","msg":"無最好既行程計劃，只有最好既心態同帶埋你既勇氣。<br />\n不過天氣不似預期今次真係啱用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1b88f09a0dea80a3720a16b721dd4c7915279de","tid":339202,"uid":29059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T00:01:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無最好既行程計劃，只有最好既心態同帶埋你既勇氣。<br />\n不過天氣不似預期今次真係啱用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n跟機g持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />加油"},{"pid":"24d43e9d6a90dd0ca55b023b7c2e35bc0535b0e6","tid":339202,"uid":48905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T01:38:35.000Z","msg":"圖呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12f63388f355115d703831a02e6727dffdf58221","tid":339202,"uid":6728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T02:41:59.000Z","msg":"等睇拉闊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0efcbbb113e8ec365018cba907def01b2e6e4a43","tid":339202,"uid":130666,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T03:30:47.000Z","msg":"終於到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好彩仲係好好天<br />\n一落機真係驚嚇 第一部atm㩒唔到錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n行到勁遠搵另一部好彩㩒到 搞埋張電話卡就坐1819出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n去到再講 未諗到去邊先"},{"pid":"030a97a7b8003065337d5a60deb4f40002e7cf36","tid":339202,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T03:31:38.000Z","msg":"去邊先第一站"},{"pid":"86c91e8de083437251bba6e1c3fae8ee2c42fd69","tid":339202,"uid":130666,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T03:45:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去邊先第一站</blockquote><br />\n放低野先啦緊係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe65239001e1801fca3aeb9921f9895214546a28","tid":339202,"uid":130666,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T03:46:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>圖呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n稍安毋躁 未開始影相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cbd494d5025c942433633f21d652a756d951ee8","tid":339202,"uid":59417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T03:53:07.000Z","msg":"圖呢樓主"},{"pid":"400133e1056f5a8103ca8238afaacd1c9cc98239","tid":339202,"uid":130666,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T08:29:56.000Z","msg":"第一站去左host到放低野，又話好近捷運站點知行左15分鐘先到，仲要上5層樓梯，不過個host超nice所以都幾好彩<br />\n上到去就沖個涼換件衫佢就話帶我去行下，人生第一次坐電單車，好爽，不過突然落雨仲愈落愈大，不過照上啦。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/29/162326_1bdbf7c2f1a735c22ee2dee8df775ad7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F29%2F162326_1bdbf7c2f1a735c22ee2dee8df775ad7.jpg&h=afb941e6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/29/162330_b8c27af5a82f2ba12c3a657e5c7747a7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F29%2F162330_b8c27af5a82f2ba12c3a657e5c7747a7.jpg&h=c9466516&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我諗唔係佢帶我上黎，呢世都唔會知有個咁既地方。<br />\n不過原本諗住出黎行下無拎相機，用re影左兩張<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/29/162455_4de5612daa5d0d41f39a9f8f6bce7430.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F29%2F162455_4de5612daa5d0d41f39a9f8f6bce7430.jpg&h=f3748ac1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/29/162459_ffdb6c0b1abb3fd51d5ea997ee14374e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F29%2F162459_ffdb6c0b1abb3fd51d5ea997ee14374e.jpg&h=bd6d523e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一個睇到全台北既地方，可惜天氣唔好同無帶相機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後約左朋友食飯，佢就車返我去捷運站。大雨到洗完頭咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nbtw個host識講廣東話，仲好中意，話講廣東話既女仔好性感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為話同台語好似。<br />\n<br />\n仲同我同星座，唔怪得咁投契<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n再續"},{"pid":"74aabf81343886dd3a8a5de2b3d94ed1fae350f4","tid":339202,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T09:08:46.000Z","msg":"劉鳴"},{"pid":"69e2cbdff42ca3950d63d8979aed8952845dbcc2","tid":339202,"uid":77661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T09:33:41.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5a74a844691cedb4c5bf686207972b9c0143e96","tid":339202,"uid":130666,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T10:55:32.000Z","msg":"咁啱朋友都係台北，所以就join埋一齊食馬辣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 馬辣歧視毒撚 一人用餐加$100 <br />\n馬辣多人到要10點先有位，所以去新馬辣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過都係要等<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/29/185120_e1e54b91b970a2d5b6a654f726df766a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F29%2F185120_e1e54b91b970a2d5b6a654f726df766a.jpg&h=eb134a55&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n個host因為驚佢今晚出去食飯飲下野太夜返，我返去個陣無人開門俾我，所以俾埋鎖鑰我，勁信任<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果唔係我約左朋友應該會同佢同佢既朋友一齊食飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n今日應該就差唔多，因為早機，勁攰，食完早啲返去抖下聽日睇下咩天氣先決定去邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家都持續落雨 今晚同聽朝好似係最勁<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/29/185341_9859b6d730bcfff3942675d639258644.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F29%2F185341_9859b6d730bcfff3942675d639258644.jpg&h=048d12e5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5827f51427b40ae5ebe2e562f2cb9cf5be5c222a","tid":339202,"uid":101991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T11:14:17.000Z","msg":"支持,畢業時都玩過一次"},{"pid":"c620d52636e512582981ddc7c931b48a08a77705","tid":339202,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T12:52:18.000Z","msg":"馬辣真係做得好成功，爆到癲"},{"pid":"1b00c0e16a9542f4f909a9d2afe9c28b141a559f","tid":339202,"uid":130666,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T13:40:39.000Z","msg":"好<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/29/213900_a723ab6d6bb2995e787ba89d9b93c4c8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F29%2F213900_a723ab6d6bb2995e787ba89d9b93c4c8.jpg&h=c1692e28&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好高質 絕對唔係百幾蚊食劣野<br />\n如果要去食一定要早兩日去訂位"},{"pid":"524fa512bf9da8cd6699a0bfcc74aa8ca35f6456","tid":339202,"uid":130666,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T15:39:14.000Z","msg":"個風打正台北 啱啱返屋企係條街到真係吹得郁我 係香港都未試過<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/29/233748_7b88a06882990e35b49c7ae4943a1327.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F29%2F233748_7b88a06882990e35b49c7ae4943a1327.jpg&h=b3425649&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n嗱嗱臨返去安全既地方訓教算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c8085452f95d0f71809203c11031e8d90c4b77e","tid":339202,"uid":130666,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T02:33:47.000Z","msg":"琴日打完風今日天氣好好<br />\n不過好似仲有個跟住黎緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/30/103017_45ab1eefd286d7ec3a82c55167350ee6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F30%2F103017_45ab1eefd286d7ec3a82c55167350ee6.jpg&h=a4eb8b5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/30/103039_ff1fecbf3a795a9d242fbc4b108f6a22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F30%2F103039_ff1fecbf3a795a9d242fbc4b108f6a22.jpg&h=caf57bf3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n諗住落去食個早餐 點知好多都無開<br />\n連m記都唔開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n見天氣咁好 暫時 個host介紹左我去望幽谷 咁就出發去下 google map話要2粒鐘<br />\n去到再講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"497f70845cd2ec46ed36cb93bc34f306ea0f7252","tid":339202,"uid":48905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T03:45:07.000Z","msg":"天氣應該又熱又焗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"899c2fc764f68576691815804bbf40b6af1ad57a","tid":339202,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T04:43:34.000Z","msg":"下個風係行南部果邊，暫時<br />\n周圍去啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d888e5204974c14e5b7636a269a9f0da94850be","tid":339202,"uid":130666,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T07:08:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>下個風係行南部果邊，暫時<br />\n周圍去啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我聽日去花蓮<br />\n想天氣好少少 而家台北都持續有雨<br />\n好驚佢停駛"},{"pid":"698e07b18d2e94648dbd3a423b01ce45a061f8f3","tid":339202,"uid":130666,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T07:09:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>天氣應該又熱又焗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同香港平時差唔多<br />\n而家仲加埋落雨"},{"pid":"7fd1db37e1e8fba3011544bde2b6b46e210255d0","tid":339202,"uid":130666,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T07:15:19.000Z","msg":"話說去到瑞芳車站諗住轉車去望幽谷個陣<br />\n個架車停駛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唯有去九份行個圈 途中突然勁大雨<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/30/151048_bc53284ecb8e750b31337c039637d074.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F30%2F151048_bc53284ecb8e750b31337c039637d074.jpg&h=52dd5893&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n影唔到有幾大雨 係好似開左花灑咁<br />\n<br />\n停低左避雨 隔離傳出喵喵聲<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/30/151233_54cb7cfc55c432ed04969e39f3847b8e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F30%2F151233_54cb7cfc55c432ed04969e39f3847b8e.jpg&h=803aa904&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n貓仔都要避雨<br />\n<br />\n之後就走啦 真係來也匆匆 去也匆匆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n跟住應該去同host食最後的晚餐 聽日出發花蓮"}]}